description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15 min Calisthenics Workout | No Equipment | All Levels' from the channel Vitality.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Check out this 15 min full body Calisthenics workout which will prepare you for skills like the human flag, planche, any lever etc. The exercises target specifically the muscle groups engaged in these Calisthenics skills.

The best is that you can do this workout at home and without any equipment! No bars, no parallettes needed. The only thing you need is yourself and motivation.

Give your best - 40 sec full energy!
